                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="15003667" author="ichattopadhyaya" created="Fri, 13 Nov 2015 07:41:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This patch adds the overridden methods to the field types.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15003887" author="cpoerschke" created="Fri, 13 Nov 2015 11:43:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;TrieDoubleField&lt;/tt&gt; change is similar to what &lt;tt&gt;TrieFloatField&lt;/tt&gt; currently has, that looks good to me.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;TrieLongField&lt;/tt&gt; change is similar to what &lt;tt&gt;TrieIntField&lt;/tt&gt; currently has, but I&apos;m wondering:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;tt&gt;TrieIntField.toNativeType&lt;/tt&gt; attempts &lt;tt&gt;Float.parseFloat&lt;/tt&gt; if the &lt;tt&gt;Integer.parseInt&lt;/tt&gt; attempt throws a &lt;tt&gt;NumberFormatException&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;in the current patch &lt;tt&gt;TrieLongField.toNativeType&lt;/tt&gt; attempts &lt;tt&gt;Float.parseFloat&lt;/tt&gt; if the &lt;tt&gt;Long.parseLong&lt;/tt&gt; attempt throws a &lt;tt&gt;NumberFormatException&lt;/tt&gt; but might &lt;tt&gt;Double.parseDouble&lt;/tt&gt; be attempted instead?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="15003911" author="ichattopadhyaya" created="Fri, 13 Nov 2015 12:13:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for looking at the patch, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=cpoerschke&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;cpoerschke&quot;&gt;cpoerschke&lt;/a&gt;. I think that is a good point, would defend against any potential precision loss in future.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15004158" author="jira-bot" created="Fri, 13 Nov 2015 15:52:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1714226 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=cpoerschke&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;cpoerschke&quot;&gt;cpoerschke&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;dev/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1714226&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1714226&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

